title.value: Cross-version VS for R5.FHIRTypes for use in FHIR R4

description.value: This cross-version ValueSet represents concepts from http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/fhir-types|5.0.0 for use in FHIR R4. Concepts not present here have direct `equivalent` mappings crossing all versions from R5 to R4.
